.SS Response
.IX Subsection "Response"
Returned by "parse_response". Croaks on unknown arguments or missing
\&\f(CW\*(C`result_type\*(C'\fR.
.ie n .IP """result_type"" \- The method name this response corresponds to" 4
.el .IP "\f(CWresult_type\fR \- The method name this response corresponds to" 4
.IX Item "result_type - The method name this response corresponds to"
.PD 0
.ie n .IP """result"" \- Hashref with result data, or undef on error" 4
.el .IP "\f(CWresult\fR \- Hashref with result data, or undef on error" 4
.IX Item "result - Hashref with result data, or undef on error"
.ie n .IP """error"" \- Hashref with ""code"" and ""message"", or undef on success" 4
.el .IP "\f(CWerror\fR \- Hashref with \f(CWcode\fR and \f(CWmessage\fR, or undef on success" 4
.IX Item "error - Hashref with code and message, or undef on success"
.ie n .IP """is_error"" \- Returns true if this is an error response" 4
.el .IP "\f(CWis_error\fR \- Returns true if this is an error response" 4
