.PD
.PP
Error codes: \f(CW\*(C`RATE_LIMITED\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`NOT_IMPLEMENTED\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`INSUFFICIENT_BALANCE\*(C'\fR,
\&\f(CW\*(C`QUOTA_EXCEEDED\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`RESTRICTED\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`UNAUTHORIZED\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`INTERNAL\*(C'\fR,
\&\f(CW\*(C`UNSUPPORTED_ENCRYPTION\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`OTHER\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`PAYMENT_FAILED\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`NOT_FOUND\*(C'\fR.
.SS Notification
.IX Subsection "Notification"
Returned by "parse_notification". Croaks on unknown arguments or missing
required fields (\f(CW\*(C`notification_type\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`notification\*(C'\fR).
.ie n .IP """notification_type"" \- \*(Aqpayment_received\*(Aq, \*(Aqpayment_sent\*(Aq, or \*(Aqhold_invoice_accepted\*(Aq" 4
.el .IP "\f(CWnotification_type\fR \- \f(CW\*(Aqpayment_received\*(Aq\fR, \f(CW\*(Aqpayment_sent\*(Aq\fR, or \f(CW\*(Aqhold_invoice_accepted\*(Aq\fR" 4
.IX Item "notification_type - 'payment_received', 'payment_sent', or 'hold_invoice_accepted'"
.PD 0
.ie n .IP """notification"" \- Hashref with notification data" 4
.el .IP "\f(CWnotification\fR \- Hashref with notification data" 4
.IX Item "notification - Hashref with notification data"
.PD
